title: Enzi: Help the economy by stopping onslaught of regulations (Michael B Enzi)
text: ( Source : Michael B Enzi ) It is often said that there are two constants in life - death and taxes, but according to U.S. Senator Mike Enzi , R-Wyo., it appears there is one more issue that Americans can't seem to escape from- regulations.
